data.text:
Here is an in-progress masterlist of all of the quests in The Dog Island. Press control-F and type in the name of the quest you want to find! Currently, they are in a random order, but it will be sorted to alphabetical once it's complete. If you can't find a quest by its name, try searching for its location or objective!
